# 🔄 LeaseLoop — Student Housing Web App

**Student housing. Simplified.**

A fast, clean web app for finding subleases, roommates, homes for sale, and new construction near universities.

## Features

- 🏠 Browse listings (subleases, roommates, homes, new builds)
- 🎯 Smart filters by campus, type, price, distance  
- ❤️ Save your favorite listings
- 📝 Post new listings easily
- 💬 Message listing posters
- 👤 User profiles
- 📱 Fully responsive

## Supported Campuses

TCU • SMU • UT Austin • Baylor • Texas A&M • UNT • University of Houston • Texas Tech

## Quick Start

```bash
python -m http.server 3000